{"name": "test_etcd_ha_failover_sglang_disaggregated", "status": "passed", "description": "\n    Test ETCD High Availability with repeated node failures and recoveries in disaggregated mode using SGLang.\n\n    This test:\n    1. Starts a 3-node ETCD cluster\n    2. Starts NATS, frontend, and both prefill and decode SGLang workers\n    3. Cycles through each of the 3 replicas:\n       - Terminate the replica by index\n       - Send inference request to verify system still works\n       - Restart the terminated node\n\n    This ensures testing of:\n    - ETCD leader termination\n    - Frontend/worker disconnection from their connected ETCD replica\n\n    Note: This test requires 2 GPUs to run decode and prefill workers on separate GPUs.\n    ", "attachments": [{"name": "log", "source": "29ac37a8-c01d-4e7d-bb6c-4c0815245434-attachment.txt", "type": "text/plain"}, {"name": "stdout", "source": "2dd3a024-23d2-4866-acdc-1c0de909adad-attachment.txt", "type": "text/plain"}, {"name": "stderr", "source": "4f4c595e-9a53-4d06-a838-2b2196d37e94-attachment.txt", "type": "text/plain"}], "parameters": [{"name": "framework", "value": "'sglang'"}, {"name": "platform", "value": "'amd64'"}, {"name": "test_type", "value": "'pre_merge_gpu'"}], "start": 1775682660320, "stop": 1775682753829, "uuid": "f3e7b838-e12b-40e1-8bd4-402b33f04c97", "historyId": "d248dc1297013ab844a0d53e027efd2d", "testCaseId": "4e44a3af7724f4968ef83af169c82729", "fullName": "tests.fault_tolerance.etcd_ha.test_sglang#test_etcd_ha_failover_sglang_disaggregated", "labels": [{"name": "dynamo_workflow", "value": "Nightly CI Pipeline"}, {"name": "dynamo_framework", "value": "sglang"}, {"name": "dynamo_platform", "value": "amd64"}, {"name": "dynamo_testType", "value": "pre_merge_gpu"}, {"name": "tag", "value": "nightly"}, {"name": "tag", "value": "e2e"}, {"name": "tag", "value": "gpu_2"}, {"name": "tag", "value": "fault_tolerance"}, {"name": "tag", "value": "sglang"}, {"name": "parentSuite", "value": "tests.fault_tolerance